name: FillStyle
desc: A style for rasterizing vector shapes.

items.name: init(eoFill: Bool, antialiased: Bool)
items.desc: Creates a new fill style with the specified settings.

items.name: var isEOFilled: Bool
items.desc: A Boolean value that indicates whether to use the even-odd rule when rendering a shape.

items.name: var isAntialiased: Bool
items.desc: A Boolean value that indicates whether to apply antialiasing to the edges of a shape.

items.name: static func == (FillStyle, FillStyle) -> Bool
items.desc: Indicates whether two fill styles are equal.

items.name: static func != (Self, Self) -> Bool
items.desc: Indicates whether two fill styles are unequal.
